Task 3
Application under test : http://zero.webappsecurity.com/
Login credentials:
Username = “username”
Password = “password”


Login Feature
Only authorized users should be able to login to the application.
1)When user logs in with valid credentials, Account summary page should be displayed.
2)Users with wrong username or wrong password should not be able to login.
3)Users with blank username or password should also not be able to login.
4)When user tries to login with invalid information, error message “Login and/or password are wrong.”
should be displayed.


Account summary Feature
1)Account summary page should have the title Zero – Account summary.
2)Account summary page should have to following account types: Cash Accounts, Investment
Accounts, Credit Accounts, Loan Accounts.
3)Credit Accounts table must have columns Account, Credit Card and Balance.


Account Activity Feature
1)Account Activity page should have the title Zero – Account activity.
2)In the Account drop down default option should be Savings.
3)Account drop down should have the following options: Savings, Checking, Loan, Credit Card, Brokerage.
4)Transactions table should have column names Date, Description, Deposit,Withdrawal.
